    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/6a0c678cf3ae2f9d93a525c646f8e635.avif?t=1751583920\" width=616 height=112 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/cfd775ddae98aad1839f07d672f29f70.poster.avif?t=1751583920\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/cfd775ddae98aad1839f07d672f29f70.webm?t=1751583920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22岁，高中同等学力毕业。<br>靠摩托送外卖艰难度日。<br>一个雨夜，你在送餐途中发生事故，邂逅了“珠熙”。<br>她介绍你到自己的咖啡厅工作，<br>在那里，你遇见了另一个总让你在意的女孩——“拿铁”。<br>这段意外的相遇，会否改变你宅男、屌丝的命运？<br>你，真的可以走向一段真挚的恋爱吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/e8bab0428b7dafeb2fe6083589526060.avif?t=1751583920\" width=616 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/67269e4f6add37b8db1acfe15dddef36.poster.avif?t=1751583920\" width=610 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/67269e4f6add37b8db1acfe15dddef36.webm?t=1751583920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>权拿铁</strong>（CV. 申温宥）<br>22岁 / 演员练习生<br>“我才和你说几句话，你就开始幻想了？”<br>说话刻薄，态度冷淡，但总是不知不觉留在你身边。<br>她的亲近是出于算计，还是隐藏着别的情感？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/66cd4e50e9c422ec3e0b3494625103a8.poster.avif?t=1751583920\" width=610 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/66cd4e50e9c422ec3e0b3494625103a8.webm?t=1751583920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潘珠熙</strong>（CV. 李明浩）<br>24岁 / 咖啡馆老板<br>“明天我们在咖啡厅见面，要带着笑哦。”<br>温柔体贴，却拼命支撑着一家快要倒闭的咖啡厅。<br>虽然对男人充满戒心，却慢慢开始对你敞开心扉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/6e80cacd7548ca3ed99166326281948b.avif?t=1751583920\" width=616 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/a3cadac88a29d4b8282de4cec2f517e4.poster.avif?t=1751583920\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/a3cadac88a29d4b8282de4cec2f517e4.webm?t=1751583920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1. 专业声优全语音 + 高品质CG</strong><br>20多张细腻的全屏CG与专业配音，演绎动人情节，感受每一丝情绪变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/1d0a190089cf1ba541021348bae53e59.poster.avif?t=1751583920\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/1d0a190089cf1ba541021348bae53e59.webm?t=1751583920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817940/extras/1d0a190089cf1ba541021348bae53e59.mp4?t=1751583920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2. 日程管理养成玩法，打造“真正的我”</strong><br>安排咖啡打工、自我提升、与女主约会等日常活动，<br>通过你的选择，引导故事走向不同的结局。</p>",
